Name:		rshaper
Version:	2.01
%define	rel	2
Release:	%{rel}
License:	GPL
Group:		Base/Kernel
Source0:	http://ar.linux.it/pub/rshaper/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
# Source0-md5:	a246d0364e5ca3de8199a0f83b758534
